\f1\b0 \
\
All inclusive versions of the GUI & Handpad eFinder programs\
Brings together all options, except for the encoder-less push-to version (ver 19)\
\
Some of the features below have been seen before, but included here for completeness or if upgrading from an early version.\
\
efinder.config now contains extra lines to specify\'85\'85\
