Ver 21 uses some changed support files, so if upgrading or trying ver21, best \ul copy\ulnone  all your existing files somewhere safe! Load all the files in the Google share ver 21 folder into your /Solver folder allowing it to overwrite when asked. Thus it will retain your subfolders and files like de421.bsp.\
\
Your Nexus DSC (Pro) will need to have the latest firmware  1.4.14 for the basic DSC and 1.1.20 for the Pro. Copies are available in the Nexus folder in the Google share.\
