\f0\b VNGUI
\f1\b0 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Has layout and font changes to improve legibility.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Has 3 new buttons\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}   Target: Reads current target RA&Dec AltAz held by the Nexus (either its own or one sent by SkySafari)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}   Set GoTo: Ability to upload a goto target to the Nexus DSC. The fields are filled with arbitrary values to demonstrate the format required.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}   Save Image: saves last captured image to the folder /Solver/Stills as filename ddmmyy_hhmmss.jpg (datetime is UTC)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If a Target has been read from the Nexus DSC, then a delta x,y with respect to the target is calculated and displayed when solving an image.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Remember delta x,y is not the same as delta Az, Alt. Delta y does equal delta Alt. Delta x equals delta Az * cos (Alt). Thus dx,dy is what would be seen in the eyepiece. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Nexus column is now a live display updated every 0.5 seconds\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}GoTo++ is now only the \'93local sync + repeat last goto\'94 version. Experience has shown this method to be excellent.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The GoTo++ function waits until the scope has finished moving before continuing, and displaying \'91goto finished\'92\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}STOP button replaces old \'91Move\'92 button, which will stop any goto in progress.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Simplified display autorotate checkbox and entry of manual image rotation.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Option to display a camera fov box, as well as eyepieces. Box size set in efinder.config. Note option to display is independent of the eyepiece fields of view \'91FOV indicator\'92\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}On starting the saved offset is now loaded.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The display of solved time is now in the scrolling report window at bottom right. This window also now includes more reports.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}While running the GUI, the handpad display shows results, and can be used to trigger solve/align/goto\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It will run without a handpad connected.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Tycho2 catalogue option removed from Annotate list. Far too many labels!\
\ls2\ilvl0{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}QHY cameras support is included, but not yet tested with an actual camera! Let me know if a problem.\
